"The Princess and the Queen\">The Princess and the Queen</a></i> <small>(2013)</small></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rogue_Prince\" title=\"The Rogue Prince\">The Rogue Prince</a></i> <small>(2014)</small></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Sons_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Sons of the Dragon\">The Sons of the Dragon</a></i> <small>(2017)</small></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Histories</td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> <small>(2014)</small></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> <small>(2018)</small></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i> <small>(2022)</small></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Blood_%26_Fire\" title=\"Blood &amp; Fire\">Blood &amp; Fire</a></i> <small>(TBA)</small></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Maps</td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-even\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Lands_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"The Lands of Ice and Fire\">The Lands of Ice and Fire</a></i> <small>(2012)</small></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible collapsed navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100